  "root_text": {
    "an9.30:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9.30 ",
    "an9.30:0.2": "3. Sattāvāsavagga ",
    "an9.30:0.3": "Āghātapaṭivinayasutta ",
    "an9.30:1.1": "“Navayime, bhikkhave, āghātapaṭivinayā. ",
    "an9.30:1.2": "Katame nava? ",
    "an9.30:1.3": "‘Anatthaṁ me acari, taṁ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṁ paṭivineti; ",
    "an9.30:1.4": "‘anatthaṁ me carati, taṁ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṁ paṭivineti; ",
    "an9.30:1.5": "‘anatthaṁ me carissati, taṁ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṁ paṭivineti; ",
    "an9.30:1.6": "piyassa me manāpassa anatthaṁ acari …pe… ",
    "an9.30:1.7": "anatthaṁ carati …pe… ",
    "an9.30:1.8": "‘anatthaṁ carissati, taṁ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṁ paṭivineti; ",
    "an9.30:1.9": "appiyassa me amanāpassa atthaṁ acari …pe… ",
    "an9.30:1.10": "atthaṁ carati …pe… ",
    "an9.30:1.11": "‘atthaṁ carissati, taṁ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṁ paṭivineti. ",
    "an9.30:1.12": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, nava āghātapaṭivinayā”ti. ",
    "an9.30:1.13": "Dasamaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "an9.30:0.1": "Numbered Discourses 9.30 ",
    "an9.30:0.2": "3. Abodes of Sentient Beings ",
    "an9.30:0.3": "Getting Rid of Resentment ",
    "an9.30:1.1": "“Mendicants, there are these nine ways to get rid of resentment. ",
    "an9.30:1.2": "What nine? ",
    "an9.30:1.3": "Thinking: ‘They harmed me, but what can I possibly do?’ you get rid of resentment. ",
    "an9.30:1.4": "Thinking: ‘They are harming me …’ … ",
    "an9.30:1.5": "‘They will harm me …’ … ",
    "an9.30:1.6": "‘They harmed someone I love …’ … ",
    "an9.30:1.7": "‘They are harming someone I love …’ ",
    "an9.30:1.8": "‘They will harm someone I love …’ … ",
    "an9.30:1.9": "‘They helped someone I dislike …’ … ",
    "an9.30:1.10": "‘They are helping someone I dislike …’ … ",
    "an9.30:1.11": "Thinking: ‘They will help someone I dislike, but what can I possibly do?’ you get rid of resentment. ",
    "an9.30:1.12": "These are the nine ways to get rid of resentment.” "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "an9.30:1.3": "acari → acarīti (sya-all) "
  },
